Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机保持距离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种速度和操控的确有威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的行动方式有一定的规律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的攻击会从正面过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要正面冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的攻击被回避掉后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止接下来的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会立刻移动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读取移动资料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S57
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种场合的下一个动作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是往后方移动保持距离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐标是X23
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看破了我们算计他的行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朱雀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO  指示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给下一步的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止的全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在布里塔尼亚有母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有家臣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有学友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说是第一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是突然而来的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本军在将人型自在战斗装甲骑KnightMare Frame
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入实战的布里塔尼亚军面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全无法抵抗而被击破了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又要被交给别的人家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是枢木的家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次要去本家那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续走  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  这种奇怪的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是在垃圾场的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会把布里塔尼亚毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在护灵车的前面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那时发誓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不原谅夺走我的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉的双眼和双腿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朱雀人生的布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了创造妹妹娜娜莉能幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把世界毁坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有都改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要公布了啊  ORANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我死了这件事就会被公开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果不想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽全力让我们逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的男人也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个男人交给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚卿  你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给他们  谁也不许出手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种计划
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘威尔卿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙的11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚卿  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了  不准出手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽全力放过他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬畏我们  追求我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的名字是  黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在有力量的人攻击没有力量的人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会再出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论那敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有多么强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有力量之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畏惧我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无力之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  由我们黑色骑士团来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲裁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要某个人胜利了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争就能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我成为了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立了黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才睡着了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样你也不用敲我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修佛德学园学生会副会长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我表面的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为布里塔尼亚学生过着无聊的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的问题就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个喜欢庆典的学生会长喜欢给人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女逆转庆典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对静音宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫祭典  还要化装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里还能容忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她说了我还是会奉陪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有那个『小学生的一天』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉看起来很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事都默许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从来到这个学园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉变的总是充满笑容了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  现在朱雀也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从7年前那个夏天以来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分别至今的朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能让他们知道我就是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果变成这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样平日的生活就会被毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不保护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geass的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只猫怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个假面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个ZERO的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把刚才看到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 该用时还是要用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是学生会长米蕾·阿修佛德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在立即去抓在校内逃窜的猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课外活动全部暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助我们的社团可以享受经费优待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来追猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赶快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  学生会长说要抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  你快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫就由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我比较擅长运动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次小鸟逃掉的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把那么久的事拿出来提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过七年前而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一如既往的体力笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明更加个人主义的才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事都在我计划的范围以内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那台白色的KnightMare出现以前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向导兵器Z01 Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用SandBoot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用最大战速沿液状斜面上升
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援总督
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀  想要问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你极端讨厌人的死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却愿意在军队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让人死才会在军队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种纯真总有一天会害死你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是吗  又是他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莲二式把白壳的家伙毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的突破力是个障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这种武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挡下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军  向撤退路线移动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再下去会成为消耗战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去追ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是能源没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特派报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始俘获
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  朱雀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想自从那时开始那家伙就改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称呼自己为『我』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明以前是自称『本人』的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\rSTAFF}[前者『僕』相对比较谦卑  后者『俺』相对比较自我主义]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在学校还是装作不认识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么去做警察  从内部改变不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的做法太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己不做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会坐收渔人之利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来改写事态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以审判者自居来得到胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话什么也改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由错误的过程得到的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到的朱雀是更加个人主义的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀着自己和日本的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率直的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此而令他泪流满面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个意义上来讲并不是全部都改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  确实有所不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要救人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想获救的是你自己的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以自己想要找死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以总是让自己前往死地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的善意只不过是自我满足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想要得到惩罚的撒娇男孩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你改变的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟有那么大的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直自己背负着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那种意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是被死板的规则所束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是成为布里塔尼亚的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是为了赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我的身边来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚已经是一个不值得你去效忠的国家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想要把它改变成有价值的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从布里塔尼亚的内部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为用错误的方法得到的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没有价值的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个小时  军事法庭就要开庭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个法庭是为了让你成为犯人而策划好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检察官也好  法官也好  辩护律师也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便那样  这也是规则
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就会开始打压11区住民和名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你会死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前  我朋友也总是这么说我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的缺点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也想抓住你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这儿反而会被反制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是要死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想为了大家而死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨拙的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从以前开始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就是因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为就是这样的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才觉得是配得上娜娜莉的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能一直陪在娜娜莉的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不是日本人 你为什么要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚的崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道能够实现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有不得不完成这事的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果按现在的计划一切顺利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要踏上去吗  修罗之路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  这是我的命运的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才需要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉能够敞开心房面对的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以信赖的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朱雀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是11 应该是叫枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是克洛维斯殿下那时的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么11在KnightMare里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终止影像  这后面的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不惜歪曲道理也要活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失望了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就按照预定把我处刑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能在那种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该在娜娜莉的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是为了这个而来到这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然落魄到成为满足现状的没出息的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使否定现在的社会也没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人承认而得到能够改变这一切的力量才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你就按那条路走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是输是赢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不使出全力是不会有任何收获的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对于国家还是个人都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO  要抓住他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木准尉Harken Boost解除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密码是我的最爱食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别继续战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的已经达成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用3号道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来回答刚才的提问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否决定了哪位来当我的骑士的提问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定的成为我的骑士的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在那里的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀要成为由菲米娅的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让搜查工作能够确实进行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个人助了我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人还说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17岁的话就应该去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:20:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时有这个权限的人是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚第三皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲米娅·Li·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以朱雀才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要救的人是由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想的话一切都合理了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选择了由菲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们  而是由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有另一招可用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经把胜利握在手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道了那个白壳的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是朱雀这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢大家长期的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次将把
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二期的OP　解読不能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及ED　モザイクカケラ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有OST CD
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节目特制电话卡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从C.C.那儿夺来的CHEESE君Q版魔方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起送给10人作为礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够参与的只有使用MVS的手机登陆手机网页
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修·Vi·布里塔尼亚下令全力的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.93,0:23:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是我的敌人?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够保护娜娜莉的男人成为了由菲米娅的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.88,0:23:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是为了保护黑色骑士团的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我来决定吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能不顾全大局吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让世界成为我所希望的样子
